  "verse_id": "10.42",
  "mūla": {
    "devanāgarī": "अथ वा बहुनैतेन किं ज्ञातेन तवार्जुन | विष्टभ्याहम् इदं कृत्स्नम् एकांशेन स्थितो जगत्",
    "iast": "atha vā bahunaitena kiṃ jñātena tavārjuna | viṣṭabhyāham idaṃ kṛtsnam ekāṃśena sthito jagat",
    "chapter_position": "Chapter 10 (Vibhūti-Yoga (The Yoga of Divine Manifestations)), verse 42",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
  },
